SUMMARY:Orchid Show &amp; Sale at Santa Rosa Veteran's Bldg.
DESCRIPTION:The Sonoma County Orchid Society presents the 2026 Orchid Show &amp; Sale\, Wild About Orchids\, a vibrant weekend celebration of these stunning blooms. Explore hundreds of orchids available for purchase from knowledgeable growers and society members\, ranging from beginner friendly varieties to rare specimens.    Guests can deepen their orchid know how through expert-led talks\, including daily sessions on how to grow and rebloom orchids\, plus a special presentation on growing and repotting Cymbidiums\, hardy outdoor orchids ideal for both beginners and experienced enthusiasts.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/orchid-show-sale-at-santa-rosa-veterans-bldg-2/2026-03-28/
LOCATION:1351 Maple Avenue, Santa Rosa, CA, 95404, United States
GEO:-122.700872;38.43443
CATEGORIES:Celebration,Family Friendly,Sonoma County
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://winecountry-media.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2026/01/17161444/487482580_1067374805431568_1105711035483199243_n.jpg
