SUMMARY:March Wine Madness at Dry Creek Vineyard
DESCRIPTION:March Wine Madness at Dry Creek Vineyard brings the excitement to the cellar because March isn’t just for basketball. For two Sundays only\, the winery’s historic cellar opens for a special open house featuring rare gems\, large-format bottles\, library wines\, mystery cases\, and exclusive finds from deep within the cellar\, some with only a few bottles remaining.    Guests can test their luck with basketball-themed games for a chance to unlock special savings or surprise extras to take home. Admission is free with a complimentary reservation requested. This casual open house allows guests to arrive at their leisure and is open to guests 21 and over only; no children or pets permitted.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/march-wine-madness-at-dry-creek-vineyard/2026-03-29/
LOCATION:3770 Lambert Bridge Road, Healdsburg, CA, 95448, United States
GEO:-122.9244491;38.6529364
CATEGORIES:Drink,Sonoma County,Wine
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://winecountry-media.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2026/01/27223328/March-Wine-Madness-2.jpg
END:VEVENT
