SUMMARY:Easter Egg Hunt &amp; Wine Tasting at Dry Creek Vineyard
DESCRIPTION:Easter Egg Hunt &amp; Wine Tasting at Dry Creek Vineyard invites guests to celebrate Easter weekend with a festive\, family-friendly experience in the heart of Dry Creek Valley.    The day begins with a relaxed Easter egg hunt on the lawn\, where children can search for eggs filled with small surprises and seasonal treats. After the hunt\, adults are invited to enjoy a seated tasting featuring a curated flight of limited-production wines\, a perfect way to sip and savor the season while the whole family takes in the beautiful spring setting.    This special gathering is limited to 12 parties to ensure an intimate and enjoyable experience. Reservations are required.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/easter-egg-hunt-wine-tasting-at-dry-creek-vineyard/
LOCATION:3770 Lambert Bridge Road, Healdsburg, CA, 95448, United States
GEO:-122.9244491;38.6529364
CATEGORIES:Drink,Family Friendly,Holiday,Napa Valley Events,Outdoors,Wine
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://winecountry-media.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2026/02/28232756/Easter-Egg-Hunt.jpeg
END:VEVENT
